{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ed3d84c592","title":"严防国民党军越过黄河进占缓德地区","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd90b8c0e7","index":0,"year":1940,"month":4,"day":1,"articleId":"ed3d84c592"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dc7965ef1f","type":"paragraph","text":"严防国民党军越过黄河进占缓德地区口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"ed3d84c592"},{"id":"c4dc8ee990","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年4月1日）确息中央军九十军李文部三个师已集中大宁。估计有该军偷进攻边区。因此请贺、关统筹我军的河防布置，无论如何不能让九十军越过黄河，这是关系八路军整个生命的问题。主震旅应加强黄部队二至三个团集结于础口附近待机，一二师平汉路东的军队是否需调若十至路西，望速决定电告[1]这是毛泽东和王荐样关于为严防国民党军题过黄河进占经德地区致朱德、彭德怀、贺龙、关向应并转王震电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"ed3d84c592"}],"page":{"id":"91c560bd00","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"ed3d84c592","start":515,"end":515}}}},"__N_SSG":true}